    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2008 Porsche Cayman S, powered by the 3.4L M97.21 flat-six engine. This mid-engine coupe offers superlative chassis rigidity and a low polar moment of inertia for surgical cornering. The 6-speed manual transmission features precise synchros and a tactile shift linkage. Equipped with the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system, the damping remains adaptive and responsive. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers over vented, cross-drilled rotors, providing excellent heat dissipation and firm pedal feel. Recent preventative maintenance includes a new water pump and an inspection of the bore scoring common to this era, showing no signs of distress. It is a sonically and dynamically pure example with minor cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage.",
